## Summary

**File edited:** `proofs/lean/extraction/Run_utf8_validation_u8Obligations.lean`

### What was added

**Helper lemmas (proved, 100% closed):**
- `RustM_ok_bind` ‚ÄĒ bind reduction for the `RustM.ok` form
- `usize_one_toNat` / `usize_two_toNat` / `usize_three_toNat` / `usize_four_toNat` ‚ÄĒ toNat of small literals (rfl)
- `usize_add_k_toNat`, `usize_no_uadd_overflow`, `usize_add_q` ‚ÄĒ `i +? k` reduces to `ok (i+k)` under no-overflow precondition
- `slice_idx_ok` ‚ÄĒ `v[i]_? = ok v.val[i.toNat]` under bounds precondition
- `u8_lt_q` / `u8_le_q` / `u8_ge_q` / `u8_eq_q` / `usize_eq_q` / `usize_ge_q` ‚ÄĒ bridge between Rust monadic comparisons and `decide`

**Step lemmas (proved, 100% closed):**
- `validate_at_oob` ‚ÄĒ `i ‚Č• size` ‚áí `validate_at v i = ok (Ok ())`
- `validate_at_ascii` ‚ÄĒ `v[i] < 128` ‚áí `validate_at v i = validate_at v (i+1)`

### Obligations status

| # | Theorem | Status |
|---|---------|--------|
| 1 | `run_utf8_validation_empty` | **CLOSED** ‚ÄĒ applies `validate_at_oob` |
| 2 | `run_utf8_validation_total` | **`sorry` with admission** |
